{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo for the point and click adventure game Crowpoint Manor, you will solve the first case where the suspect is Samuel the Swimmer who is a guest at Crowpoint Manor.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore the eerie grandeur of Crowpoint Manor, a sprawling estate filled with rooms that hold more than meets the eye. From a circus performer with a penchant for danger to a botanist with rather aggressive Venus flytraps, each resident poses a new challenge.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pick-up-and-play gameplay: Easy to start, but once you step into Crowpoint Manor, it\u2019ll be hard to leave.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tons of puzzles: Navigate a mansion full of twisted brain teasers and darkly humorous interactions.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A thrilling dark comedy: Experience a story dripping with wit, as each accident brings you closer to solving the mystery\u2014or becoming the next victim.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Atmosphere you won\u2019t forget: Crowpoint Manor is a place where the absurd meets the eerie, and nothing is quite as it seems.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Will you outwit the guests, uncover the killer, and survive your stay at Crowpoint Manor? Or will your investigation end with dessert?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732295935","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359800/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732295935","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359800/874c07d1327788cc9a3d45250e60926c0b57e628/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=17322